{"tid":757607,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美眾院通過國防授權法案 限中國對美投資","createTime":"2018-07-27T03:59:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T12:41:35.000Z","uid":141151,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"73ac687ad468bc27565a0d1c5de9393f858be4f2","tid":757607,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T03:59:30.000Z","msg":"美眾院通過國防授權法案 限中國對美投資<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/stock/article/1900762\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2FinstantnewsMob%2Fstock%2Farticle%2F1900762&d=m6Tl1wlmNK78WziCMXKRX0zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=536cc6b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnewsMob/stock/article/1900762</a><br />\n<br />\n美國眾議院通過法案，內容包括加強限制中國等外來投資。<br />\n<br />\n美國眾議院以359票贊成、54票反對，大比數通過7160億美元國防授權法案。<br />\n<br />\n該法案旨在控制中國對美國投資，及禁止美國政府使用中國主要電訊設備企業的技術。法案還增強美國外資審議委員會(CFIUS)的權力，此舉主要針對中國。CFIUS負責審查外商投資計劃，以評估這些交易是否存在國家安全憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n法案稍後仍須獲參議院批准。<br />\n<br />\n該法案基於國家安全憂慮而包含控制美國政府與中興通訊(00763)和華為合約的措施，但相關限制的力度遠不及最初起草的版本。"},{"pid":"6246f5f3f9dd04efcf98c782656dc922e5dddf7e","tid":757607,"uid":13663,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T04:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/120007_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F120007_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=5e938e3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48459a21dc9e9c69ce5eb750cac03cb7d0917e27","tid":757607,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T04:01:21.000Z","msg":"屎為打手入黎講幾句"},{"pid":"8d1513eb93fb62c1638939d3d103682712645cef","tid":757607,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T06:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ba2c069508d3174ecba6e9a048696e4ff9f05b","tid":757607,"uid":162